author: Anjana George
title: Malayalis have good music sense: Deepak Dev
text: According to music composer Deepak Dev, music sense and taste of Keralaites has been evolving for the past few years. "This transition was what I was exactly waiting for. Our people have become more open and also accepting the global style. This gives us, musicians more inspiration to jam more and bring out more!" he goes effusive.
